text: <!channel> the community cycling center is doing a really cool promotion right now if anyone needs a new bike bag and some bike parts <http://www.communitycyclingcenter.org/index.php/pack-a-pannier-sale-25-off-everything-inside-the-bag/>
Love that promotion. If you've got a frame kicking around, you can nearly build a bike on the cheap from the parts bins that way.
